        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1956-03-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1956-03-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="515"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d515">
                <head>515. Telegram 1585 from Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d515fn1"
                        >Source: Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/3–356. Official Use
                        Only; Priority. Originally received as telegram 1538 but corrected to 1585.
                        Repeated for information Priority to Prague for Ambassador <persName
                            corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName> as telegram 26.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Geneva</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1956-03-03"
                            >March 3, 1956, 11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d515-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d515-1"/>
                <p>1585. From Osborn.</p>
                <p>According information from reporters, statement being released at (repeat at)
                    Chinese Communist Consulate General 3:30 p.m. local time today.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GFC_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Gowen</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
